        "body": "Talking with Jason about resolves that need other resolves as input. For example:\r\n\r\n```\r\n            resolve: {\r\n              'a': {...},\r\n              'b': (a) => {...},\r\n            }\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis pattern is supported by AngularJS routers, but not supported in Angular Router. We need to at least document that limitation and suggest workarounds."
